<normalizedToken id="CE0821A0E1F63DDE9DD2F008B6A23A0F" originalValue="Weiße" pageId="null" pageNumber="487">Weisse</normalizedToken>
Lupine
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
</title>
<subSubSection id="757AB0F23BB45FFC33D9498BE57272F7" pageId="null" pageNumber="487" type="description">
<paragraph id="E163BCEF68F7E2CDADE39DCB069F7E73" pageId="null" pageNumber="487">
1 
<normalizedToken id="7D3CCB03643C5E8F308F610607F11FC2" originalValue="jährig" pageId="null" pageNumber="487">jaehrig</normalizedToken>
; 20-120 cm hoch. 
<emphasis id="FCD9D61F76C715E1E5FA7144E1310448" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="487">
<normalizedToken id="87FF1B6DE15C2FF7D801C15E6C3066EA" originalValue="Teilblätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="487">Teilblaetter</normalizedToken>
5-9
</emphasis>
, lanzettlich, 2-6 cm lang und 
<emphasis id="451B894ADBF138F967E95B172368FA09" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="487">0,8-1,8 cm breit</emphasis>
, spitz, unterseits anliegend behaart (Haare 0,7-1,8 mm lang), oberseits fast kahl. 
<normalizedToken id="37851DAB4FE3DF7CF483757DA84C4C22" originalValue="Blütenstand" pageId="null" pageNumber="487">Bluetenstand</normalizedToken>
5-10 cm lang, fast ungestielt. 
<normalizedToken id="C8FB4346E5541242971903283B978B75" originalValue="Blüten" pageId="null" pageNumber="487">Blueten</normalizedToken>
<normalizedToken id="E136072B99B815C2DE9D4A068348052F" originalValue="wechselständig" pageId="null" pageNumber="487">wechselstaendig</normalizedToken>
. 
<emphasis id="21D1D2AA1ACFE51517F7CCBE130FFCFF" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="487">
Krone 1,5-2 cm lang, 
<normalizedToken id="B7DC2FA58E73364E01720BF22D558217" originalValue="weiß" pageId="null" pageNumber="487">weiss</normalizedToken>
</emphasis>
, selten hellblau. Frucht 3-6 cm lang und 0,6-1 cm breit, anliegend behaart. Samen 
<normalizedToken id="37D1FFB84509C65FBE916BCF1C30B6F7" originalValue="linsenförmig" pageId="null" pageNumber="487">linsenfoermig</normalizedToken>
, 9-14 mm lang. - 
<normalizedToken id="23D578D11186250C80DBD8C752E5998E" originalValue="Blüte" pageId="null" pageNumber="487">Bluete</normalizedToken>
: 
<normalizedToken id="0F5D2C22A73F158CA1679C6441C9B981" originalValue="Frühling" pageId="null" pageNumber="487">Fruehling</normalizedToken>
und Sommer.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="CEC156866B02BCDED62E3177679E72B0" pageId="null" pageNumber="487">
<emphasis id="C443BBC09A3442F1C572CD31B4D03249" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="487">Zytologische Angaben. 2n</emphasis>
= 
<emphasis id="2796583987E7402578C2C0DEC61804F5" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="487">30</emphasis>
(Olszewska 1954). 
<emphasis id="17F2471BF52A4CBF1860CE45D56F2CFD" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="487">2n</emphasis>
= 
<emphasis id="643454E6370B4C5BE72206F0816FC76E" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="487">40</emphasis>
und 
<emphasis id="37A7D8EEF1F99B79AE02D4E3B460978F" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="487">48</emphasis>
(Savchenko aus Darlington und Wylie 1955). 
<emphasis id="45679A56AF9A19A7A5F8597B05B1E848" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="487">2n</emphasis>
= 
<emphasis id="9F87B777793126EE75EA657EE99E1334" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="487">50</emphasis>
(Tuschnjakov aus Olszewska 1954; Malheiros 1942, Atabekova 1959, Gilot 1965). Alles Material unbekannter Herkunft.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="225DC0CAEE230F7B09A5EB9BE41AA58E" pageId="null" pageNumber="487">
<emphasis id="3FAF7ABD03520CB5DE48F4DABD714B2C" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="487">
<pageBreakToken id="00930413B53BF730DF93CCC8681FA033" pageId="null" pageNumber="487">Standort</pageBreakToken>
.
</emphasis>
Kollin. Felder, unbebaute Orte in warmen Lagen.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="484070B17C22013018F0514FE0C6CA4C" pageId="null" pageNumber="487">
<emphasis id="BD3342FF3EB855AE4C3B108ED25A4260" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="487">Verbreitung. Mediterrane Pflanze. -</emphasis>
Im Gebiet (besonders im 
<normalizedToken id="41509034D5044412F797252E31DD884E" originalValue="Süden" pageId="null" pageNumber="487">Sueden</normalizedToken>
) bisweilen als Futterpflanze angebaut und selten verwildert.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
